[20:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'would look like a few frames into the future. And if there\'s sparse data, like if there\'s a certain point that doesn\'t contain a lot of image data, then it also uses cross-temporal pairing and street view interpolation, so basically'

[20:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'use AI to fill in the blanks. Now, like I said, currently they\'ve only trained this on the streets of Seoul, Korea, but you know, this is a really fascinating idea. We could extrapolate this to other places in the world to build like a'

